LandingPageHabitsText: Develop new habits by tracking your progress over 10, 100 or even 1,000 days! You can adjust the frequency of each particular habit to suit you. For example, it's possible to do something at intervals ranging from 1 to 100 days.
LandingPagePreferencesText: Or maybe all you need to do is just keep track of your preferences and interests? For example, with the goal of discovering what you would actually be interested in trying to explore more thoroughly. Or simply to find a new hobby to help brighten up your free time. Whatever the reason, there's nothing stopping you from keeping summary statistics on your preferences!
LandingPageSkillsText: Another skill you're so eager to improve? With the right approach, it's no problem! Try adjusting your success rate and minimum requirements for the ideal ratio to improve each day! Also, don't forget to track your progress, either for each specific skill or all at once.
